{"id":590,"date":"2023-07-16T08:34:25","date_gmt":"2023-07-16T15:34:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/?page_id=590"},"modified":"2024-04-18T21:11:51","modified_gmt":"2024-04-19T04:11:51","slug":"the-particle-%e3%81%ae%e3%81%bf","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/the-particle-%e3%81%ae%e3%81%bf\/","title":{"rendered":"The Particle\u00a0\u306e\u307f\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Particles \u306e\u307f\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The particle \u306e\u307f is very similar to \u3060\u3051. One of the main things to keep in mind is that it is not \u306e\u306b.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Adverbial Particle \u306e\u307f<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u306e\u307f has fallen into more so literary usage due to the rise of \u3060\u3051. \u306e\u307f has&nbsp;four&nbsp;distinct usages.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Limits something to a certain amount.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u306e\u307f\u3060 shows that at&nbsp;<em>that<\/em>&nbsp;much, there is no other situation.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u306e\u307f\u304b means &#8220;not just that&#8221;.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u306e\u307f\u306a\u3089\u305a means &#8220;not only&#8221;.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;<strong><u>Examples<\/u><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. \u3053\u306e<ruby>\u6751<\/ruby>\u306e\u307f\u304c<ruby>\u6c34\u5bb3<\/ruby>\u306b\uff5b\u514d\u308c\u305f\u30fb<ruby>\u906d<rt>\u3042<\/rt><\/ruby>\u308f\u306a\u304b\u3063\u305f\uff5d\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Only this village escaped the damages from the flood.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><ruby>2. \u795e<\/ruby>\u306e\u307f\u305e<ruby>\u77e5<\/ruby>\u308b\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Only God knows.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>3. \u6211\u3005\u306f\u305f\u3060<ruby>\u5fcd\u8010<rt>\u306b\u3093\u305f\u3044<\/rt><\/ruby>\u304c\u3042\u308b\u306e\u307f\u3060\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; We only have perseverance.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><ruby>4. \u5165\u5834<\/ruby>\u306f<ruby>\u62db\u5f85\u8005<\/ruby>\u306e\u307f\u53ef&nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Admission by invitation only<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><ruby>5. \u8001\u5175<\/ruby>\u306f<ruby>\u6b7b<\/ruby>\u306a\u305a\u305f\u3060<ruby>\u6d88<\/ruby>\u3048<ruby>\u53bb<\/ruby>\u308b\u306e\u307f\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Old soldiers never die, they just fade away.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><ruby>6. \u5bcc\u58eb\u5c71<\/ruby>\u306f\u305f\u3060<ruby>\u9ad8<\/ruby>\u3044\u306e\u307f\u306a\u3089\u305a\u3001<ruby>\u7f8e<\/ruby>\u3057\u3044\u306e\u3067\u3059\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Mount Fuji is not just tall, but it is also beautiful.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>7.<ruby>\u5263\u8853<rt>\u3051\u3093\u3058\u3085\u3064<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306e\u307f\u304b<ruby>\u4e16\u6545<rt>\u305b\u3053<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306b\u3082<ruby>\u9577<rt>\u305f<\/rt><\/ruby>\u3051<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;Not only know about fencing, but also know about worldly affairs.&nbsp;<br>From \u6c60\u6ce2\u6b63\u592a\u90ce<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>8a. \u3053\u306e<ruby>\u6c34\u65cf\u9928<\/ruby>\u306b\u306f\u3001<ruby>\u6df1\u6d77\u9b5a<\/ruby>\u306e\u307f\u306a\u3089\u305a\u3001<ruby>\u71b1\u5e2f\u9b5a<\/ruby>\u3082\u3044\u307e\u3059\u3002(A little old-fashioned)<br>8b. \u3053\u306e<ruby>\u6c34\u65cf\u9928<\/ruby>\u306b\u306f\u3001<ruby>\u6df1\u6d77\u9b5a<\/ruby>\u3060\u3051\u3067\u306a\u304f\u3001<ruby>\u71b1\u5e2f\u9b5a<\/ruby>\u3082\u3044\u307e\u3059\u3002(More natural)<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; In this aquarium, there are not only deep-sea fish but also tropical fish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Grammar Note<\/strong>: Using \u3060\u3051\u3067\u306a\u304f is much more common because, again, \u306e\u307f is very literary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>9.&nbsp;<ruby>\u7dca\u6025<rt>\u304d\u3093\u304d\u3085\u3046<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306e<ruby>\u5834\u5408<\/ruby>\u306b\u306e\u307f<ruby>\u9023\u7d61<\/ruby>\u305b\u3088\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; Call me in only in the case of an emergency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>10.&nbsp;<ruby>\u6c34\u4e0d\u8db3<rt>\u307f\u305a\u3076\u305d\u304f<\/rt><\/ruby>\u306f\u3044\u3088\u3044\u3088<ruby>\u6df1\u523b<\/ruby>\u3060\u3002<ruby>\u5f8c<\/ruby>\u306f\u305f\u3060<ruby>\u96e8<\/ruby>\u304c<ruby>\u964d<\/ruby>\u308b\u306e\u3092<ruby>\u5f85<\/ruby>\u3064\u306e\u307f\u3060\u3002<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The water shortage is really serious. The only thing to do is wait for it to rain.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Particles \u306e\u307f\u00a0 The particle \u306e\u307f is very similar to \u3060\u3051. One of the main things to keep in mind is that it is <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/imabi.org\/the-particle-%e3%81%ae%e3%81%bf\/\">\u7d9a\u304d\u3092\u8aad\u3080 <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">&#8220;The Particle\u00a0\u306e\u307f\u00a0&#8220;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":158153075,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"advanced_seo_description":"","jetpack_seo_html_title":"","jetpack_seo_noindex":false,"jetpack_post_was_ever_published":false,"footnotes":""},"tags":[],"class_list":["post-590","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"jetpack_likes_enabled":true,"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/PeXUlI-9w","jetpack-related-posts":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/590","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/158153075"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=590"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/590\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4963,"href":"https:\/\/imabi.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/590\/revisions\/4963"}],"wp:attachment":